                <div class="company-context">Deep learning research at Silicon Valley R&D lab</div>
                <div class="details">
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>Novel Architectures:</strong> Developed custom CNN autoencoders for wireless CSI compression, addressing a critical bottleneck in 5G/6G networks.</li>
