                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>Financial Platform Development:</strong> Led end-to-end development of FinX, a mission-critical financial API serving 5,000+ employees across European operations, collaborating with DBMS, testing, and deployment teams.</li>
                        <li><strong>Cross-Platform Integration:</strong> Integrated FinX with Outlook, JIRA, SharePoint, and Confluence, implementing automated workflows that cut expense approval times by 50%.</li>
                        <li><strong>Data Engineering:</strong> Generated Business Intelligence extracts from 17+ database tables and optimized report generation, reducing query time by 30%.</li>
                    </ul>
